data.title: Samuel Dalembert Player Profile, Dallas Mavericks
data.meta_description: Get the latest news, stats and more about Samuel Dalembert on RealGM.com
data.text: Jun 27, 2001 - The Philadelphia Sixers selected Samuel Dalembert in Round 1 with Pick 26 in the 2001 NBA Draft. Aug 6, 2001 - Samuel Dalembert signed a multi-year contract with the Philadelphia Sixers. Oct 24, 2003 - The Philadelphia Sixers exercised their Team Option to extend the contract of Samuel Dalembert. Jun 28, 2005 - The Philadelphia Sixers tendered a Qualifying Offer to make Samuel Dalembert a Restricted FA. Jul 1, 2005 - Samuel Dalembert, previously with the Philadelphia Sixers, became a free agent. Aug 2, 2005 - Samuel Dalembert signed a multi-year contract with the Philadelphia Sixers. Jun 17, 2010 - Samuel Dalembert was acquired by the Sacramento Kings from the Philadelphia Sixers in exchange for Spencer Hawes and Andres Nocioni. Jul 1, 2011 - Samuel Dalembert, previously with the Sacramento Kings, became a free agent. Dec 9, 2011 - The Sacramento Kings renounced their free-agent exception rights to Samuel Dalembert. Dec 26, 2011 - Samuel Dalembert signed a multi-year contract with the Houston Rockets. Jun 27, 2012 - Samuel Dalembert was acquired by the Milwaukee Bucks, along with a 2012 1st round pick (HOU own), a conditional 2014 2nd round pick (HOU own) and cash, from the Houston Rockets in exchange for Jon Brockman, Jon Leuer, Shaun Livingston and a 2012 1st round pick (MIL own). Jul 1, 2013 - Samuel Dalembert, previously with the Milwaukee Bucks, became a free agent. Jul 11, 2013 - The Milwaukee Bucks renounced their free-agent exception rights to Samuel Dalembert. Jul 19, 2013 - Samuel Dalembert signed a multi-year contract with the Dallas Mavericks. Jun 25, 2014 - Samuel Dalembert was acquired by the New York Knicks, along with Jose Calderon, Wayne Ellington, Shane Larkin, a 2014 2nd round pick (DAL own), a 2014 2nd round pick (BOS own), cash and a TPE, from the Dallas Mavericks in exchange for Tyson Chandler and Raymond Felton. Jan 5, 2015 - The New York Knicks placed the contract of Samuel Dalembert on waivers. Jan 8, 2015 - Samuel Dalembert, previously with the New York Knicks, became a free agent. Jul 31, 2015 - Samuel Dalembert signed a contract with the Dallas Mavericks. Oct 24, 2015 - The Dallas Mavericks placed the contract of Samuel Dalembert on waivers.
